description: Best damn BBQ west of Texas, that's what it is! Smoke City BBQ serves up delicious, juicy BBQ to the streets of LA! With the tastes of Texas in Southern California, Smoke City BBQ is taking over with their great ribs, brisket, and more. All meats smoked with white oak for a minimum of 15 hours. It is the most succulent tender meat you've ever put in your mouth. All it takes is one try and you're hooked!
name: Smoke City BBQ on Wheels
